原因： 首先，大多数书显然不可能在一天之内、一口气读完。因此，在每本书的阅读周期内，我们随时都有可能发现新的、感兴趣的书籍。我认为，排斥或拖延这种兴致是完全没有必要的。阅读兴致稍...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":810,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"如何阅读一本书","slug":"如何阅读一本书","count":5,"path":"api/categories/如何阅读一本书.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"阅读","slug":"阅读","count":6,"path":"api/tags/阅读.json"}],"author":{"name":"桌沿","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://imgs.zhubai.love/c6dfb4dd470244c5bb0835469b9d9781.png","link":"/","description":"桌沿奇思 Newsletter 主理人，少数派签约作者","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"sspai":{"icon":"/svg/sspai.svg","link":"https://sspai.com/u/379wzx2e/posts"},"newsletter":{"icon":"/svg/newsletter.svg","link":"https://deskside.zhubai.love"},"jike":{"icon":"/svg/jike.svg","link":"https://okjk.co/IktPrE"},"mailto":{"icon":"/svg/mailto.svg","link":"mailto:deskside.zhuoyan@outlook.com"}}}},"feature":true}}